## Modules\
Call read_me again with the modules parameter to load detailed guidance:\
- `diagram` \'97 SVG flowcharts\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  structural diagrams\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  illustrative diagrams\
- `mockup` \'97 UI mockups\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  forms\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  cards\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  dashboards\
- `interactive` \'97 interactive explainers with controls\
