**Backgrounds**: `--color-background-primary` (white)\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  `-secondary` (surfaces)\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  `-tertiary` (page bg)\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  `-info`\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  `-danger`\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  `-success`\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  `-warning`\
