### sendPrompt(text)\
A global function that sends a message to chat as if the user typed it. Use it when the user's next step benefits from Claude thinking. Handle filtering\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  sorting\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  toggling\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  and calculations in JS instead.\
