### Metric cards\
For summary numbers (revenue\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  count\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  percentage) \'97 surface card with muted 13px label above\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  24px/\cf7 \strokec7 500\cf4 \strokec4  number below. `background: var(--color-background-secondary)`\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  no border\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  `border-radius: var(--border-radius-md)`\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  padding 1rem. Use in grids of \cf7 \strokec7 2-4\cf4 \strokec4  with `gap: 12px`. Distinct from raised cards (which have white bg + border).\
