### Layout\
- Editorial (explanatory content): no card wrapper\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  prose flows naturally\
- Card (bounded objects like a contact record\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  receipt): single raised card wraps the whole thing\
