**Grid overflow:** `grid-template-columns: 1fr` has `min-width: auto` by default \'97 children with large min-content push the column past the container. Use `minmax(\cf7 \strokec7 0\cf2 \strokec2 ,\cf4 \strokec4  1fr)` to clamp.\
